  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_2' aria-label=\" Mala Devi versus Union of India & Ors. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('2','2025','2025_8_221_228','2025INSC855'); ><font size='4'> <strong>MALA DEVI<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>UNION OF INDIA & ORS. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 8 S.C.R. 221</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 855</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010003142025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : SANJAY KAROL<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, SATISH CHANDRA SHARMA</strong><br> Issue for Consideration Whether in the facts and circumstances of the case, the Appellant is entitled to family pension of her late husband, and whether a denial of such relief was justified. Headnotes&dagger; Indian Railway Establishment Manual &amp; the Railway Pension Rules, 1993 &ndash; Appellant&rsquo;s husband, a temporary employee with the Eastern Indian Railways died in harness &ndash; Claim of the Appellant for family pension was denied on the ground that it is not admissible to the wife of an employee whose services were not regularized &ndash; Justifiability: Held:<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 16-07-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 10672/2016</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Appeal(s) allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_8_221_228','2025INSC855','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_8_221_228','2025INSC855','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('2','2025','2025_8_221_228','2025INSC855');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('2','2025','2025_8_221_228','2025INSC855','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
